Invocation Name: fact book
des:
Knowing about facts is always interesting and engaging. This application was developed keeping in mind of thing how we can develop our young generation interest to know about the interesting facts of our body, life, space, food and existence. 

This is a simple Do you know Fact Alexa skill that tells user about interesting facts.
